      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "UNSTOPPABLE MIST (1) broke well and quickly mustered speed to win over the 365m at this track two runs back then raced on speed again when finishing second at this track last start. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Top chance in this line up. ZULU SHARP (7) could manage only third but ran quick time (24.75) at Goulburn over 440m. Harder here but expected to feature again. FLY HIGH HENRY (2) turned in a fair run last time from an unfavourable draw finishing fourth by 2.75 lengths (21.03). Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Can figure in the finish. MAXIMUM GAYLE (4) can measure up with the right run.",
